Federal Minister of Labour Hubertus Heil (SPD) wants to review other sectors in accordance with the strict regulations now planned against maladministration in the meat industry.
"We will look at industry by industry and then take appropriate measures for the respective industry if necessary," said Heil of the German Press Agency in Berlin.
